{"tid":2020224,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"NASA 數十位科學家只用了短短37天就研發好可快速批量生產的呼吸機 以應對供應不夠的問題","createTime":"2020-05-17T01:43:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T02:39:51.000Z","uid":28114,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"077c0667c844345055c90c7cad9d76290c8805d5","tid":2020224,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T01:43:03.000Z","msg":"NASA設計呼吸機 貨運太空船離開國際太空站<br />\n<br />\n世界各地的科研人員都在與新冠病毒作鬥爭，這一努力延伸到了一個加班加點地幫助地球病人的太空飛行實驗室。<br />\n<br />\n星期一，天鵝座貨機離開國際太空​站。它之前於2月18日到達那裡，送去了數噸重的供給品和科學實驗用品。<br />\n<br />\n美國太空總署​說，告別國際太空​站後，天鵝座現在會幫助進行火情探測其他付費運輸。<br />\n<br />\n不過，本週的重頭消息來自美國太空總署​位於加州帕薩迪納的噴氣推進實驗室，簡稱JPL。在那裡，機電一體化工程師米歇爾&middot;伊斯特Michelle Easter等數十位科學家創建了一種稱為VITAL（也叫可就近接觸的呼吸機干預技術）的呼吸機系統。<br />\n<br />\n美國太空總署​機電工程師米歇爾&middot;伊斯特說：&ldquo;這是一種基層的自發性的努力，為幫助應對新冠病毒危機時刻呼吸機供應不夠的情況。而我們做出的設計是一種低成本、容易、快速批量生產的呼吸機。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n科研人員在短短37天內設計並建造了VITAL系統。<br />\n<br />\n伊斯特說：&ldquo;這對不管開發任何工程產品來說都是非常短的時間，尤其是達到我們這種研發、測試，並獲得批准的水平。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n食品藥物管理局(FDA)在呼吸機&ldquo;緊急使用授權&rdquo;政策下於4月30日批准了VITAL原型，這有助於該項目快速上馬。美國宇航局向有能力生產該產品的製造商免費提供設計圖。伊斯特現在在新冠疫情的混亂中看到了希望。<br />\n<br />\n伊斯特說：&ldquo;有各種各樣的人在加大力度召集有關組織來嘗試並尋找解決方案，這確實讓人受到激勵和鼓舞。這種幫助提醒所有人，我們同舟共濟。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nVITAL這種設備是由宇航局的JPL設計和製造的兩個模型中的第一個。伊斯特說，另一個更新的模型可以隨時準備就緒，裡面帶一個像打理花園用的鼓風機的馬達。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voacantonese.com/a/nasa-builds-covid-ventilator-delivery-vessel-says-goodbye-to-iss20200515/5422040.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voacantonese.com%2Fa%2Fnasa-builds-covid-ventilator-delivery-vessel-says-goodbye-to-iss20200515%2F5422040.html&d=5MMtl3Q8rD8%2FKomM%2B8e61%2F8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=3bac8ea8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voacantonese.com/a/nasa-builds-covid-ventilator-delivery-vessel-says-goodbye-to-iss20200515/5422040.html</a>"},{"pid":"5cd88e0440127f669b49a85766f4ee1e66a730e8","tid":2020224,"uid":220451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T01:53:29.000Z","msg":"Sir this way"},{"pid":"91dd923c5612975d99dd6a1b83cc2b1c1f2958e0","tid":2020224,"uid":28114,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T01:57:22.000Z","msg":"USA 🇺🇸 USA 🇺🇸 USA 🇺🇸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9c158ba272745af0f4a1142429cb1b4330aa1e9","tid":2020224,"uid":155095,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T01:59:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/202005/02d53764be89b1033ea2f5604ec3f05a.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F202005%2F02d53764be89b1033ea2f5604ec3f05a.JPG&h=b29f9ea3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2630000/2634114/job_18_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2630000%2F2634114%2Fjob_18_1024.jpg&h=4f7c4243&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2630000/2632302/0501012_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2630000%2F2632302%2F0501012_1024.jpg&h=8e33a2e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"732dc837a1942eaf6c3ec884df90b5c13c262a7a","tid":2020224,"uid":291921,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T02:10:13.000Z","msg":"NASA wor<br />\n太空船都識整啦<br />\n人地係科技上不嬲都係最頂尖<br />\n入得去做既都係最top有真材實料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你估大陸咩，俾錢買個名同位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1eba311addc3a78f77f3c2db62e44c1ac33382c","tid":2020224,"uid":33336,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T02:13:53.000Z","msg":"寜願花資源整呼吸機，都唔整口罩"},{"pid":"4371d02d2630000b600064ada52f2eab8d69a65a","tid":2020224,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1eba